How It Works

Exchange services without money in four simple steps

Step 1: Create Profile

Sign up and list your skills and services you can offer to others.

Step 2: Discover Services

Find services you need offered by people in your neighborhood.

Step 3: Propose Exchange

Offer your service in exchange for theirs and agree on details.

Step 4: Build Reputation

Complete exchanges and build your community reputation.

No money changes hands. Just skills and services!
